body:
Hello, I am a French first language living in Quebec. I have been playing for almost 4 years in my second language. I would really like a French option because I think it will be easier for me. Also, I have a friend who speaks almost only French who just started the game and has trouble understanding. I am tired of translating for them and would really like an easy way for both of us and anyone else who speaks French primary to play.
(sorry for bad english) {{champion:114}} {{item:2050}} 

Thanks.
